data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET DUE TO NO FAULT OF THE SELLER - WELL KEPT HOME IN DESIRABLE NEIGHBORHOOD, CLOSE TO POST, EATERIES, SHOPPING AND I-295. WHEN YOU WALK IN THE FRONT DOOR YOU ARE WELCOMED WITH A DINING ROOM TO YOUR LEFT AND STAIRCASE TO YOUR RIGHT, THE MAIN BEDROOM IS LOCATED DOWNSTAIRS TO THE RIGHT OF THE GREAT ROOM AND FEATURES A JETTED TUB AND SEPARATE SHOWER, LARGE WALK IN CLOSET. THE GREAT ROOM FEATURES A VAULTED CEILING. THE LARGE KITCHEN FEATURES LARGE PANTRY, HALF BATH, LAUNDRY ROOM WITH UTILITY SINK AND AN EAT IN AREA WHERE YOU CAN WALK OUT ONTO YOUR SCREEN PORCH AND ENJOY YOUR MORNING CUP OF COFFEE ON THOSE PLEASANT MORNINGS. UPSTAIRS FEATURES AN OFFICE SPACE, BONUS ROOM/BEDROOM AND 2 OTHER BEDROOMS THAT ARE A NICE SIZE.
